		<part id="conclusions">
			<title>Conclusions</title>
			<slide id="consumption">
				<title>API Consumption Matters</title>
				<ul>
					<li>Digital transformation needs <em>digital building blocks</em></li>
					<li>Digital building blocks need to be <em>useful and usable</em></li>
					<li>Useful building blocks clearly document <em>the value they bring</em></li>
					<ul>
						<li>Usable building blocks expose the value as easily consumable APIs</li>
					</ul>
					<li>Value is an integral part of all API marketing activities</li>
				</ul>
